  "detailed_description": "Detective Northwood gets assigned by the FBI to investigate a chemical company for the suspicion of a terrorist attack on the city, but the company he is investigating belongs to one of the most important figures in the whole country.<br>But that won’t stop him , as he knows the risk is too high to begin worrying about politics.<br>He will break every bone and spill every drop of blood and kill if he has to ,to save the souls of innocent people.<br><br>-Dynamic combat. <br>-Fatality finishes. <br>-challenging gameplay.<br>-amazing graphics.<br>-realistic fighting moves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/4fb44265199496673aa5f5dd7d1a19ca.poster.avif?t=1623350584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/4fb44265199496673aa5f5dd7d1a19ca.webm?t=1623350584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/4fb44265199496673aa5f5dd7d1a19ca.mp4?t=1623350584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/7b8960abe7a8938b22411ea811870bcf.poster.avif?t=1623350584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/7b8960abe7a8938b22411ea811870bcf.webm?t=1623350584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611110/extras/7b8960abe7a8938b22411ea811870bcf.mp4?t=1623350584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c